WEBVTT

00:07:57.955 --> 00:08:00.970
my parents did not own a phone line.

00:08:01.986 --> 00:08:04.835
Today, my two sons --

00:08:08.408 --> 00:08:10.462
David and Daniel,

00:08:10.486 --> 00:08:15.052
can talk to my parents
and get to know them.

00:08:17.917 --> 00:08:20.703
Why should we allow

00:08:20.727 --> 00:08:27.622
such a wonderful, brilliant
and necessary product

00:08:27.646 --> 00:08:31.581
to be the cause of unnecessary suffering